description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 2:

The View co-hosts Hostin and Navarro test positive for covid, removed from set live on TV before Kamala interview. Biden hasn't had his booster. Chris Cuomo's former boss accuses him of sexual harassment incident 16 years ago, Cuomo admits it happened. Female callers react to Cuomo story.
